        The noble and learned Lord, Lord Woolf, wanted a simplified and combined set of rules giving effect to the clear objectives he defined in his reports. The object of this amendment would be to keep the committee, which one hopes will meet, up to the mark, and require it to publish information about its doings. I beg to move.
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0575P0-05788'>
        <a name='S5LV0575P0_19961120_GCR_89'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-james-mackay' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0575P0_19961120_GCR_89' title='Link to this speech by Mr James Mackay' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
