          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-james-mackay" title="Mr James Mackay">The Lord Chancellor</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I simply confirm that it is not my intention to alter the present law and so I am happy to consider these matters further.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0575P0-05876'>
        <a name='S5LV0575P0_19961120_GCR_177'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-alexander-irvine' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
