        <q>Page 3. line 43, after second ("Court") insert&#x2014;</q>
        
        <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_41gc' title='Col. 41GC &mdash; HL Deb 20 November 1996 vol 575 c41GC' name='column_41gc' href='#column_41gc' rel='bookmark'>41GC</a>
