      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0575P0-05891'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0575P0_19961120_GCR_192' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">The Lord Chancellor</span> moved Amendment No. 33:
        <q>Page 6, leave out lines 37 to 42 and insert&#x2014;</q>
        <q>("( ) for subsections (5) and (6) there is substituted&#x2014;</q>
        <q>(5) Special rules may apply&#x2014;
        <ol>
        <li>(a) any rules made under this section, or</li>
        <col>CWH 42</col>
