        <span class="member">The Lord Chancellor</span> moved Amendment No. 34:
        <q>Page 6, line 43, leave out from ("(9)") to end of line and insert ("for "Supreme Court Rule Committee" there is substituted "Civil Procedure Rule Committee" ").</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0575P0-05895'>
